@NODE INTRODUCTION "About FindFile"


  You d'not know where is your file, only run FindFile and FOUND this,
  if you have it.

  FindFile is a utility to search for eny programm if you give a letter
  between 1 or more character and if find eny name same with input name
  then keep this in memory and give information about size, blobks,
  date,protection and the full path of name to by found.


@ENDNODE INTRODUCTION

@NODE INSTALL "Install FindFile"





                 Copy the files where you want and that is.
		 FindFile runing immentiately


@ENDNODE INSTALLATION

@NODE USEKEY "Using Keys"

		This programm only controled with keyboard.


	Keys are:
		(P/p) - Pause searching and go in select mode,
			or return in main.
	        
		(Q/q) - Quit programm for main only.
		
		(Esc) - Escape for eny mode and return in main,
			or quit programm.

	   (SpaceBar) - Pause searching and go in select mode,
			or return in main.

	     (Return) - Information about file with full name,
			and return main.
	
  (arrow key Up/Down) - Move up/down bar file where found.


	Mouse using only for click in left corner to quit programm,
        or rong parameters.

@ENDNODE USEKEY

@NODE USING "Use FindFile"
   FindFile use three (3) parameters but two (2) is using obligingly
   

  Syntax: FindFile  <Path> <Search Name> <Buffer>

	  Path  -  The Device or Drawer to begin start searching

   Search Name  -  The Name if you know or letter for searching
		   (For greek user searching only for up or lo case
		   character in this moment.If search for name (Exa)
                   find only names if have only - (E) - character).
		   For other user search any case of character.

        Buffer  -  Buffer to scan drawer.Buffer is optional.
		   Internal Buffer it whose in (800) and enough
		   for serching about 90-240 MB.
		   Largest Buffer is (32767) but for this you want
		   about (1.1-1.5 MB) of memory to use programm,
		   for internal Buffer want about (130-240 KB).
@ENDNODE THEAUTHOR

